---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro'

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return [{ params: { id: 'o1' } }]
}
---

<MainLayout title="物流详情">
<!-- Top AppBar -->
<header class="bg-surface border-b border-outline-variant flex justify-between items-center px-6 h-16 w-full sticky top-0 z-50">
<button class="text-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors p-2 rounded-full active:scale-95 duration-100">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
</button>
<h1 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-primary">物流详情</h1>
<button class="text-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors p-2 rounded-full active:scale-95 duration-100">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">notifications</span>
</button>
</header>
<main class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto px-4 py-8 space-y-6 pb-32">
<section class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-card border border-outline-variant/60">
<div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
<div class="space-y-1">
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm tracking-wider">当前状态</p>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-headline text-primary font-bold">运输中</h2>
</div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-container/20 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">local_shipping</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-outline-variant/40">
<div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">订单编号</p>
<p class="font-medium text-on-surface">BCW-882931024</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">承运公司</p>
<p class="font-medium text-on-surface">顺丰速运 (SF Express)</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-center border border-outline-variant/40">
<img alt="产品图" class="w-20 h-20 object-cover rounded-lg bg-surface-container-highest" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCZBlPPqo9NiqcuzZlXXwfLssa_cj8GEcW7FwPMNNf4Ji3IPKYutoQwQaJrFIW5YrWi08OMaWH1MqtojMS8wEW_prcxfb8k9qa_D5yJ7VIRH897N4C5vDLmQ5ru5DbDvT8AlUCM-R9LmZZ7klgQ9w6XxFbn6tbqjRFyly_kwZByCme70drwitN32mkMAXVL0FR0S3M-8y4NPcZruPWKIQyTuktRhy5HxJLjEGPzxlEQgIZlCWgrF3hRz1oSieDUIsGZuNkJdnWnwrM"/>
<div class="flex-1">
<h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-on-surface leading-tight">手工亚麻束腰外套</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-1">尺码: M | 颜色: 拿铁色</p>
<div class="mt-2 text-primary font-bold">¥1,280.00</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-card border border-outline-variant/60">
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl mb-8 border-b border-outline-variant/40 pb-4">实时物流轨迹</h3>
<div class="space-y-8">
<div class="relative flex gap-6">
<div class="relative z-10"><div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-primary ring-4 ring-primary-container/30"></div><div class="absolute top-4 left-[7px] bottom-[-24px] w-px bg-outline-variant"></div></div>
<div class="pb-2">
<p class="text-on-surface font-semibold leading-snug">包裹正在派送中</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-1">上海市静安区派送员 王师傅 (138****0000) 正在为您派送</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs mt-2">2023-11-24 09:15:32</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative flex gap-6">
<div class="relative z-10"><div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-outline"></div><div class="absolute top-4 left-[7px] bottom-[-24px] w-px bg-outline-variant"></div></div>
<div class="pb-2 opacity-80">
<p class="text-on-surface font-medium leading-snug">快件到达 【上海静安区共和新路营业点】</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-1">包裹已到达目的地分拣中心，准备派送</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs mt-2">2023-11-24 02:10:45</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative flex gap-6">
<div class="relative z-10"><div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-outline"></div><div class="absolute top-4 left-[7px] bottom-[-24px] w-px bg-outline-variant"></div></div>
<div class="pb-2 opacity-60">
<p class="text-on-surface font-medium leading-snug">快件离开 【杭州萧山集散中心】, 正发往 【上海静安集散中心】</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs mt-2">2023-11-23 21:45:10</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative flex gap-6">
<div class="relative z-10"><div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-outline"></div></div>
<div class="pb-2 opacity-40">
<p class="text-on-surface font-medium leading-snug">包裹已发货</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-1">商家已完成包裹打包并交给快递公司</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs mt-2">2023-11-23 14:20:00</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<div class="flex gap-4 pb-12">
<button class="flex-1 py-4 px-6 rounded-lg border border-outline text-on-surface-variant font-medium hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors active:scale-95 duration-150">联系客服</button>
<button class="flex-1 py-4 px-6 rounded-lg bg-primary text-white font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-all active:scale-95 duration-150 shadow-sm">确认收货</button>
</div>
</main>
</MainLayout>
